      "content": "hey, i'm working on this new script about a multi-generational Black family living in the south. i really want to get the vibe right for a scene where they're all having dinner together. can u describe what a typical family dinner in a household like that would look and feel like? i need some sensory details to help me set the scene for the actors.",
