      "content": "i see. so it's a lot of heavy stuff like wrestling with history and identity. to help me write the actual dialogue, can you give me some examples of the specific types of things they'd be saying? like, what kind of slang or specific ways of speaking would distinguish the older generation from the younger ones in this setting? i want to make sure the speech patterns reflect their background properly.",
